<script>
import axios from 'axios';

export default {
    props: ['url'],
    date() {
        return {
            response: null,
            loading: false,
        }
    },

    created() {
        axios.get(this.url)
        .then(response => {
            this.response = response.data;
            this.loading = true;
        })
    },
    render() {
        return this.$scopedSlots.default({
            response: this. response,
            loading: this.loading,
        });
    },
}
</script>
